videos.description:
Romeo Santos - The Making of 'Propuesta Indecente' (Vevo Footnotes)

Watch music videos by Romeo Santos: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyxbZF7_PK4nLiexj0kkCNg

El 2014 fue un a├▒o estelar en la m├║sica latina, pero fue Romeo Santos quien se alz├│ victorioso con uno de los lanzamientos m├бs esperados por los fans de la bachata: su canci├│n тАЬPropuesta IndecenteтАЭ. тАЬQuer├нa crear algo distinto con un elemento que nunca antes se hab├нa fusionado a la bachataтАЭ, dijo Santos en entrevista exclusiva. тАЬSe me ocurri├│ el tango. La tem├бtica ten├нa que ser sensual, atrevida, y as├н naci├│ [la canci├│n]тАЭ. La pegajosa mezcla entre el tango y la bachata finalmente puso el g├йnero en la consciencia global, convirtiendo a Santos en el segundo artista latino en la historia en lograr un bill├│n de vistas en YouTube. El bachatero tambi├йn arras├│ en las listas cuando тАЬPropuesta IndecenteтАЭ se convirti├│ en la primera canci├│n en permanecer por 100 semanas en el Billboard Hot Latin Songs durante el 2015. El video, filmado en Buenos Aires por el director Joaqu├нn Cambre, es una joya visual: una historia de seducci├│n en la pista de baile con aires de pel├нcula noir. Hablamos con Romeo Santos, quien no s├│lo di├│ detalles curiosos detr├бs de las c├бmaras de тАЬPropuesta IndecenteтАЭ, sino tambi├йn sobre el impacto del lanzamiento en su carrera. Todo esto en el nuevo episodio de Footnotes. 

2014 was a stellar year for Latin music, but it was Romeo Santos who came out on top with one of bachataтАЩs modern cornerstones: тАЬPropuesta Indecente.тАЭ тАЬI wanted to create something different with an element that had never been fused with bachata,тАЭ Santos said in our exclusive interview. тАЬI thought about tango. The theme was sensual and daring - thatтАЩs how the song was born.тАЭ The catchy fusion between tango and bachata finally put the genre on the global map, turning Santos into the second Latin artist in history to reach one billion video views. The superstar also killed it chart-wise, making тАЬPropuesta IndecenteтАЭ the first track to ride BillboardтАЩs Hot Latin Songs chart for 100 consecutive weeks. The video, filmed in Buenos Aires by director Joaqu├нn Cambre, is a visual gem тАУ a story of seduction on the dancefloor, shot film noir style. We spoke with Santos who gave us behind the scenes details while addressing the impact тАЬPropuesta IndecenteтАЭ had on his career. All of this and more on the newest episode of Footnotes.

Romeo Santos, Chris Lebron - The Making of 'SIRI' (Vevo Footnotes)

El Rey de la Bachata, Romeo Santos, toma su t├нtulo de manera literal. Una de sus obras maestras, тАШF├│rmula Vol.2тАЩ, sali├│ en el 2014 y permaneci├│ en la lista Billboard Top Latin Albums por 386 semanas consecutivas, m├бs que ning├║n otro disco de bachata hasta la fecha. Nada f├бcil la maroma. En su follow-up, тАШF├│rmula Vol.3тАЩ, el bachatero se dedic├│, no s├│lo a sorprender a sus fans con influencias de hip-hop, R&B, y hasta comedia, sino tambi├йn a levantar el perfil de nuevos talentos como Chris Lebr├│n, artista invitado en тАЬSIRIтАЭ. Sobre la colaboraci├│n, Lebr├│n dice que desde que supo que тАЬten├нa esta responsabilidad de entregar un proyecto a Romeo, mi mente empez├│ a maquinar muy r├бpidoтАЭ. Tras bromear en el estudio con un amigo, Lebr├│n invoc├│ a la omnipresente Siri en su celular para que le resolviera sus problemas de amor. тАЬDe ah├н en adelante, fluy├│ todoтАЭ, dijo. videos.title: Dream Productions | Available December 11 on Disney+
videos.description:
From the world of Inside Out comes #DreamProductions ЁЯОе available December 11 and in 2025 comes #WinOrLose ЁЯеО available February 19, only on Disney+.

ABOUT тАЬDREAM PRODUCTIONSтАЭ
Taking place in between the events of тАЬInside OutтАЭ and тАЬInside Out 2,тАЭ тАЬDream ProductionsтАЭ is an all-new series about the studio inside RileyтАЩs mind where dreams really do come trueтАФevery night, on time and on budget. Riley is growing up and when her memories need some extra processing, Joy and the rest of the Core Emotions send them to Dream Productions. Acclaimed director Paula Persimmon (voice of Paula Pell) faces a nightmare of her own: Trying to create the next hit dream after being paired up with Xeni (voice of Richard Ayoade), a smug daydream director looking to step up into the big leagues of night dreams. Also featuring the voices of Amy Poehler, Maya Rudolph, Ally Maki, Kensington Tallman, Liza Lapira, Tony Hale, Lewis Black and Phyllis Smith, the hilarious, mockumentary-style series is written and directed by Mike Jones and produced by Jaclyn Simon.
 
ABOUT тАЬWIN OR LOSEтАЭ
тАЬWin or LoseтАЭ reveals what it actually feels like to be in the shoes of eight different characters in the week leading up to the big gameтАФthe insecure kids, their helicopter parents, even a lovesick umpireтАФwith incredibly funny, very emotional and uniquely animated perspectives. Featuring the voice of Will Forte as the coach, тАЬWin or LoseтАЭ is directed, written and executive produced by Carrie Hobson and Michael Yates, and produced David Lally.

videos.title: ЁЯФ┤[LIVE DELAY] Debat Publik Perdana Pilkada Sulawesi Utara
videos.description:
Komisi Pemilihan Umum (KPU) Provinsi Sulawesi Utara berhasil menggelar debat terbuka pertama Pilgub 2024 pada Rabu, 9 Oktober 2024 lalu. Debat dilaksanakan di Kota Kotamobagu dengan tema 'Pemberdayaan Ekonomi Lokal, Ketahanan Pangan, Pariwisata, Pengelolaan Sumber Daya Alam, dan Tata Ruang Berwawasan Lingkungan.'

Adapun Pilkada Sulut diikuti oleh Mantan Kabainstrahan Kemhan Mayjen TNI (Purn) Yulius Selvanus-Johannes Victor Mailangkay dengan nomor urut 1. Kemudian paslon mantan Bupati Kepulauan Talaud sekaligus ayah dari anggota DPR RI Hillary Brigitta Lasut, Elly Engelbert Lasut-Hanny Joost Pajouw nomor 2. Dan petahana wakil gubernur, Steven Kandouw-Letjen TNI (Purn) Alfred Denny Tuejeh di nomor urut 3.

Hey, art friends! Welcome to Art For Kids Hub! ЁЯОитЬПя╕П

Here, you'll discover all sorts of awesome art lessons, from drawing to painting, and even some super cool origami. Whether you're a beginner or a budding artist, there's something fun for everyone!

I'm Rob, and along with my amazing wife, Teryn, and our four creative kids, Jack, Hadley, Austin, and Olivia, we make art together as a family and love sharing it with you. тЭдя╕П

Ready to jump in and start creating? Most of our art lessons are self-contained, so grab your favorite black marker, some paper, and your coloring supplies, and let's get drawing! ЁЯЦНя╕ПЁЯУТ

Join us on this colorful adventure, and let's make art that brings smiles and joy. Happy creating! ЁЯМЯ

The electrons in an atom are arranged in shells that surround the nucleus, with each successive shell being farther from the nucleus. Electron shells consist of one or more subshells, and subshells consist of one or more atomic orbitals. Electrons in the same subshell have the same energy, while electrons in different shells or subshells have different energies. https://fundraise.samaritanspurse.org/fundraiser/5855888
 
Guys we left Florida to get away from hurricane Helene but it hit North Carolina so much worse! We did what we could to help bring supplies the first few days but this area will need a lot more help for years to come. Many of the major roads were blocked off and there was no way to get emergency supplies in to them. for the first five days after the hurricane many people were able to stay alive from the airdrops that the community had organized. We rented a super small plane so we could help bring supplies in to the areas that were hit the worst.

channel.name: NLE CHOPPA
channel.description:
NLE Choppa, the 20-year-old Memphis MC, has already made waves in the rap game with over 5.5 billion streams, 14 RIAA-certified plaques, and two Billboard Hot 100 singles in 2023. His recent album, Cottonwood 2, further solidifies his place as a superstar. Despite his success, Choppa remains dedicated to his fans and continues to push boundaries. videos.title: Which Sabretooth Actor Was The BEST?
videos.description:
Tyler Mane and Liev Schreiber both took on the role of Sabretooth, though in different film series. Tyler Mane portrayed the character in "X-Men" (2000) as well as in "Deadpool and Wolverine," bringing a raw and imposing physicality to the role. Meanwhile, Liev Schreiber played Sabretooth in "X-Men Origins: Wolverine," offering a more nuanced and conflicted take on the character. Each actor brought their own unique interpretation to Sabretooth, contributing to the character's rich and varied depiction across the X-Men film universe, but which is the superior Sabretooth portrayal? videos.description:
Stephen KnightтАЩs moody atmospheric examination of BirminghamтАЩs gang life between world wars has come to its sixth and final season and its brought with it the symbolism and attention to telling the story through set design. The gang of street fighters from the working class neighborhood of Small Heath has gone scrapping  for the scraps of the horse betting to having a patriarch Thomas Shelby serving as an MP in Parliament. Regardless of holding public office, it turns out thereтАЩs no amount of legit the ShelbyтАЩs and the Peaky Blinders canтАЩt seem to break free of the violence that brought them to power in the first place. For the last season a lot of those chickens are coming to roost for the first family of Birmingham some of their darkest sins are bound to revisit them. Horse imagery and color selection have been employed to outline and reinforce the story of the family that fought for it all only to find they could not stop fighting no matter how successful. There are playful easter eggs reflecting on the previous five seasons as well as playful ways that the people who make the show get themselves in it. The season looks back to create a sense of closure from the first shot to the final shot and setting up the promised feature length film that will bring the story from the end of World War I to World War II. videos.title: 20 Things You Missed In The Bob's Burgers Movie
videos.description:
FoxтАЩs Sunday night Animation Domination block has had another one of its breakaway shows breakaway into a big screen adaptation, this time Lauren BouchardтАЩs BobтАЩs Burgers: The Movie. After 12 seasons the creators were tasked with the no small task of creating a love note to the fans that have supported the show all these years while still making a movie that can be enjoyed by someone who has never watched the show before. Just like the quirky and one of a kind show it's based on, the movie sidestepped many of the flashy elements weтАЩve become accustomed to when a franchise tries to jump from one market to another. Instead they focused on the things that have made the show unique, from its look to its already colorful cast and mythology. The result is the first Disney animated film to be a hand-drawn two dimensional affair with no gimmicky guest spots or even gratuitous cameos from recurring characters unless they moved the story forward. By design the viewer is given everything they need to know in the first five minutes of the movie, but if you have been watching all this time youтАЩll be reunited with characters and character details that have helped make BobтАЩs Burgers the hit it's become. The Belchers end up on an adventure that is bigger than the TV screen yet just as familiar. Let us know your favorite callback in the movie in the comments and while youтАЩre there be sure to like and subscribe for the latest in your inbox.
